== Module: monit
Manages the monit daemon, http://mmonit.com/monit/
Currently it supports only process monitoring.

== Notice:
In order to use this module two global variables must exist:
* +$LOCAL_SMTP+ - the fqdn of you smtp server
* +$ROOT_MAIL+  - the email-address where notifications go

